main.c: 

    g_main_context_new() in g_thread
    - MainLoop: GMainLoop
    - ThreadLoop: g_thread from g_main_loop_new()


main_with_while_loop.c (what we want):

    g_main_context_default() in main thread
    - MainLoop: while loop
    - ThreadLoop: g_thread from g_main_loop_new()


